Resurrection of Christ. From this composition - with the stone rolled away (but with the angel omitted) a drawing by Hans Bol is developed see Brian Koetser Gallery Exh. of Old Master Drawings, [London], May - June 1976, N°. 27 Hans Bol [...] 'This drawing derives from the same series as the 'Adoration of the Shepherds' that was in the collection of Kurt Meissner, [Françoise Forster-Hahn, Old Master Drawings from the Collection of Kurt Meissner, Zürich, Stanford (Calif.): Dept. of Art, Stanford University, 1969], cat. N°. 48 (also signed and dated 1571).'
